rComments: Really passionate about the course she teaches. She makes excellent use of powerpoint slides and other forms of multimedia, such as videos and films. Very eye-opening lecturer, and the material is not difficult to understand. It is easy to do well in this class as long as you show up to lectures and study from the course pack.
Easy course. Good teacher. You can sense the vicarious experience of hardships when she speaks.

Great class, very informative and eye-opening. Go to lecture because she shows many YouTube and PBS clips and asks questions about them on the test. The course reader is used a lot, read the articles and know the main points. The tests were easy, just attend lecture, read articles thoroughly.
Really helpful and passionate about the material. Helps you to succeed.
